data.description: This 1976 Sq ft, 4 bedroom 2 bath Mobile home sits on permanent foundation in a well established neighborhood in Judsonia. This home features full solar energy, large walk in closets, garden tub and separate shower in the master bath, spacious split floorplan, large shop with 2 overhead doors and electric, storm shelter, fenced in yard and so much more. Title has already been canceled! New owners will have to assume solar financing.
